            {
                "moduleIds": [
                    1
                ],
                "content": "<p>Try It Out!</p><p>This workflow automates a recurring SOL transfer and posts a real-time confirmation message to a Discord channel. It moves SOL from your AFK Crypto wallet to a Phantom wallet and then notifies Discord with the amount, status, and a direct link to the blockchain transaction:</p><p></p><p>Use cases are many: Automate SOL payouts, create transparent payment logs for teams, or send periodic transfers with instant confirmation in Discord:</p><p></p><p>How it works:</p><p></p><p>24 Hours trigger starts the workflow every day.</p><p></p><p>Set Transfer Details defines the sender, recipient, transfer amount (in Lamports), and the Discord webhook URL.</p><p></p><p>Send SOL Transfer node calls AFK Crypto’s /send API to execute the transfer.</p><p></p><p>Discord node posts a structured confirmation message, including transfer details and the transaction hash.</p><p></p><p>How to use:</p><p></p><p>Replace YOUR_WALLET_HERE with your AFK Crypto wallet address.</p><p></p><p>Replace YOUR_RECEPIENT_HERE with the recipient wallet address.</p><p></p><p>Update amount in Set Transfer Details (remember, 100,000,000 Lamports = 0.1 SOL).</p><p></p><p>Add your Discord webhook URL to the discordWebhookUrl field.</p><p></p><p>Activate the workflow to start sending SOL and Discord confirmations every 24 hours.</p><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><p></p><p>AFK Crypto account and API key</p><p></p><p>Phantom or Solana-compatible wallet address</p><p></p><p>Discord account and webhook URL</p><p></p><p>🔔 Seamless SOL Transfers with Instant Discord Alerts!</p>",
                "isFilterNote": false,
                "metadata": {
                    "color": "#9138FE"
                }
            }
        ]
    }
